What is Jenkins ?
Jenkins is an oss automation tool written in java with pluggins built for cicd purpose.

Define the process of Jenkins 
commit the changes
detect source code changes
the bbuild either passes or fails
generate feedback

what are the benefits of using jenkins
cache build failures
automate build report notification
achieve ci
automation of maven project
easy tracking of bugs

what is the use of pipeline in jenkins
pipeline is pluggin is used in jenkins pipeline, which gives us the view of stages or
tasks to perform one after the other in the pipeline form

expalin the terms agent, post-section, jenkinsfile
agent is to tell jenkins to execute the pipeline in a particular manner and order

post-section needed to add some notification and to perform other tasks at the end of a pipeline

what is trigger? 
triggers are used to define when and how pipelines should be executed

